nhc_headline: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS INTO A CATEGORY 2 HURRICANE WELL TO THE SOUTH OF BAJA CALIFORNIA...
summary: ...NARDA STRENGTHENS INTO A CATEGORY 2 HURRICANE WELL TO THE SOUTH OF BAJA CALIFORNIA... As of 8:00 PM MST Tue Sep 23 the center of Narda was located near 15.3, -109.4 with movement W at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 972 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 100 mph.
